reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect collection of pens, pencils, and highlighters
reviews.reviewText: This little zipper pouch is so esthetically pleasing. The selection of colors for the highlighters are so pretty. I oddly like the square shape of the marker. All the pens write in black, not the color of the outside of the pen. I knew this when I ordered, but figured I would disclose here if someone else thinks differently. The pens are very smooth and write nicely. Even the texture of the actual pen is nice. The pouch fits perfectly into my work bag. I am just over all very pleased with this pouch!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for annotating books for beginners!!
reviews.reviewText: I bought this because I wanted to start annotating my books for the first time. I found this kit and it had everything that I would need to start, so I bought it and I am impressed. The highlighters are not dark, they're a light pastel color, perfect for annotating. I didn't have much issues with them bleeding into the book pages. I only made a few small accidental marks after leaving it in one place for a couple seconds too long but after a couple pages of practice, I did not have that issue anymore. The pens are all black ink, and they write really smooth. They are a perfect pitch black and I haven't run into any issues with them yet. They also did not pass through the pages (of course that depends on how hard you press it into your page). The mechanical pencils are really easy to write with, too. The erases work perfectly (not like the gritty erasers that erase horribly and just leave your paper weak and ready to rip). It also came with pen and pencil refills that I really appreciated because I hate having to hunt for refills. The actual pencil case itself is small but spacious.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2023
